haberman.rhizomatics.data

Class Vector2

  • java.lang.Object
    • haberman.rhizomatics.data.Vector2
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable

    public class Vector2
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable
    Encapsulates a 2D vector. Allows chaining methods by returning a reference to itself. Also contains static methods for computing vector math.
